Package com.authenticket.authenticket.model

Class Admin

java.lang.Object
com.authenticket.authenticket.model.Admin
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, org.springframework.security.core.userdetails.UserDetails
@Entity public class Admin extends Object implements org.springframework.security.core.userdetails.UserDetails
The `Admin` entity represents an administrative user. This entity is used for administrative users in the system and implements the `UserDetails` interface for Spring Security integration.
